<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">والدِّلِّيْلَى:</span> الدَّليل، ومنه قولُه<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">في الحديث:</span> <span class="c2">«اقْبَلُوا هُدَى اللهِ ودِلِّيْلَاه»</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
